'''天主教（帕拉的）貝倫總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Belemensis de Pará}}；{{lang-pt|Arquidiocese de Belém do Pará}}）是[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]在[[巴西|巴西]]的一個教省[[總教區|總教區]]。此總教區下轄7個教區和1個自治監督區<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 06.11.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/06/191106b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-11-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107055643/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/06/191106b.html |archivedate=2019-11-07 |language=en |date=2019-11-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

總教區位於[[帕拉州|帕拉州]]東北部六市，2006年有教友1,503,302人，佔轄區總人口73.6%。教區下轄五十四個堂區，有132名司鐸。現任總主教為{{link-en|亞爾伯·塔維拉-科雷亞|Alberto Taveira Corrêa}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 30.12.2009 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/12/30/0822/01956.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-11-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107100740/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/12/30/0822/01956.html |archivedate=2019-11-07 |language=it |date=2009-12-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-de|安多尼·達-阿西斯-里貝羅|Antônio de Assis Ribeiro}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 28.06.2017 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/06/28/170628c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-11-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107101225/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/06/28/170628c.html |archivedate=2019-11-07 |language=en |date=2017-06-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1720年3月4日成立教區，直屬[[天主教里斯本宗主教區|里斯本宗主教區]]。1906年5月1日升為總教區。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arquidiocesedebelem.org.br/index2.html |title=Dados Históricos |access-date=2013-11-13 |archive-date=2014-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625224828/http://www.arquidiocesedebelem.org.br/index2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

